_sText: aim_ag_tyr3 ----------- 12 players Description: My third skill map. It is set within a small arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. This map is not focused on horizontal gunfights. By adding a second floor another dimension of strategy is used. I made this map to my own design. Objective: Use the objects, height and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve...
